creator: Appscape Studios
descriptionHtml:
Make your friends (or yourself) smile, groan, or laugh out loud with our puns and corny jokes.

Our clean jokes are family friendly! You can safely share our jokes with your family, coworkers, kids, peers, students! If they lol at corny humor, they'll enjoy our joke app.

Our hilarious jokes are appropriate for everyone.

We've hand picked a list of all the best jokes for our joke book app!

When someone asks you "tell me a joke", you can open our joke book and laugh out loud at our funny, clean jokes.

Laugh out loud at corny humor with our joke book! We have:
• puns
• dad jokes
• kid jokes
• corny jokes
• clean jokes
• one-liners
• cheesy jokes
• lame jokes
• punny jokes
• amusing jokes
• anti jokes
• witty jokes
• funny jokes

Features of the "Pun Intended: Dad Jokes, Funny Puns, Corny Jokes" app include
- Browsing puns by swiping left and right
- Creating a list of your favorite jokes
- Share a funny joke with friends or family via the convenient share button (you can choose text or image format)
- Sending feedback easily through our interface
- Enjoying colorful backgrounds

Features coming soon
- Liking and disliking puns
- Searching for puns you like
- Categories

How to send feedback for our corny jokes app

Encountered problems with our joke book app? Having trouble swiping through puns? Have corny joke suggestions? Please let us know by emailing appscapes@gmail.com . We want to hear your feedback on our cheesy joke app.

About Appscape Studios

We pride ourselves on producing high quality apps, such as this dad joke app, to fill people's daily lives with joy, laughter, and puns!
descriptionShort: Want to laugh? Our joke book has the best jokes, puns, dad jokes, & corny jokes
